  "name": "Integrated genome-wide investigations of the housefly, a global vector of diseases reveal unique dispersal patterns and bacterial communities across farms",
  "author": {
    "name": "Simon Bahrndorff",
    "givenName": "Simon",
    "familyName": "Bahrndorff",
    "affiliation": {
